# REACT NATIVE INTALLATION OF DEPENDENCIES

## if Linux system then prefix these commands with sudo

#### to clear cache memories

expo start -c

#### to install npm packages

npm install 

or 

expo add yarn 

#### to install react native elements

npm install react-native-elements

##### for yarn 

yarn add react-**native**-elements

#### if the saving of any particular file is not allowed in mac specially then eg App.js

**sudo chmod  777 App.js** 

Sudo chmod -R 777 name of folder/



 #### To start the expo cli tool





expo start

yarn add react-**native**-elements # or with npm npm install react-**native**-elements



